title: Jiaqi Zhang | 张嘉琦
snippet: Jiaqi Zhang is a PhD candidate in the Department of Computer Science at Brown University, working with Dr. Ritambhara Singh on single-cell analysis and multi-modal integration. He has published several papers on graphical model structure estimation, gene network, and cell developmental dynamics.

title: About me (CV) - Jiaqi Zhang
snippet: Jiaqi Zhang is a mathematician who works on numerical algorithms for complex physical problems. He has published papers on dynamic wetting, interfacial flows, brain concussion, and solidification, and has received grants from NSFC and GBASF.

title: Jiaqi Zhang - zjiaqi2018.github.io
